{"tid":1508832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於機場 我有啲野想講！","createTime":"2019-08-26T15:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T22:42:48.000Z","uid":264174,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f77b7aabdbe225aec281338cece398d747ea0920","tid":1508832,"uid":264174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:39:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>機場係春袋<br />\n機場係春袋<br />\n機場係春袋</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">事先講明唔係冷氣軍師 6月到依家都成日去發夢<br />\n由和理非變左做半個勇武</span><br />\n其實由前日已經有人講要入機場圍機場<br />\n但好多人話荃葵青等咗好耐 又有不反對通知書 點都要去遊行唔入機場<br />\n又話唔好再叫人去機場 因為會分散曬啲人<br />\n好 就比大家行埋琴日 勇武埋琴日<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">但大家勇武過後冷靜諗一諗</span></span></strong><br />\n如果琴日真係比大家打贏 啲狗走曬啦<br />\n個目的係？霸住晒啲路 癱瘓交通有咩用？<br />\n逼政府回應？咁同去返雨傘有咩分別？<br />\n點解啲狗突然咁好死呢兩日都批不反？<br />\n你以為佢地真係轉死性？ 唔好意思 你諗得太簡單<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地識圍魏救趙<br />\n你估佢地唔識？<br />\n依家擺到明唔想我地去搞春袋</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">812咁多人入機場<br />\n有冇手足送頭？冇<br />\n有冇放催淚彈？冇<br />\n係一啲事都冇啊</span></span><br />\n嗰次柒婆仲要即刻衝出黎回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解啊？<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>因為我地做岩咗囉</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解大家仲要諗？！<br />\n見到前日同琴日有咁多手足送頭 真係好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你話我機場撚又好 點都好<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>求下大家一齊入機場啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\nP牌仔講野 推唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家覺得有道理就幫推啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bS0iXRm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbS0iXRm.png&h=73e92862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AMUf7VF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAMUf7VF.jpg&h=0b85483a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xy7UD2m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXy7UD2m.jpg&h=c9ad4316&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tBZvWO2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtBZvWO2.jpg&h=267c835c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d7940cde0cd01dcb948159dcae268dc5d73f793","tid":1508832,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:40:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">求幫推</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最新post 睇得清楚d + 加左明天有義士再審係頂！</span></span>(極正經)(請推至長期置頂)被捕義士進程，一個也不能少不只是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7b94ff78a99f7c662b0e775f4d8fa5946f1fb7ef","tid":1508832,"uid":264174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:44:35.000Z","msg":"求幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"200c18c22e3ef9e4a7d802c49b07ef1be1d1584c","tid":1508832,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:45:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=q